He called a couple of days ago
and he left a message.

13:38.310 --> 13:40.812
(crying)
and he sounded upset.

13:40.813 --> 13:43.948
(Alan) but we never
found out why.

13:45.718 --> 13:47.218
(Esposito) tough one?

13:47.219 --> 13:48.820
Yeah.
They're all tough.

13:48.821 --> 13:50.354
So you got anything?

13:50.355 --> 13:52.323
Yeah, Vixen's alibi
checked out.

13:52.324 --> 13:54.325
We've been talking
to Crow's coven friends

13:54.326 --> 13:56.327
And searching through
vampire web sites.

13:56.328 --> 13:57.862
So far, no Daemon.

13:57.863 --> 13:59.296
What about Lockerby?

13:59.297 --> 14:01.933
Morgan Lockerby--
psychiatric disorder,

14:01.934 --> 14:03.735
35, committed by the state.

14:03.736 --> 14:05.236
That's the good news.

14:05.237 --> 14:07.739
Bad news is,
he escaped a few years back.

14:07.740 --> 14:10.441
Nobody's seen him since.
Got an address on file?

14:10.442 --> 14:13.211
No. He's completely off grid.

14:13.212 --> 14:15.179
What's your shadow doing?

14:15.180 --> 14:17.148
I don't know.
Last time I saw him,

14:17.149 --> 14:20.417
he was sifting through evidence
from Crow's apartment.
Hmm. So are you going?

14:20.418 --> 14:22.653
To what?
His Halloween party.

14:22.654 --> 14:26.224
I don't know. He throws
a lot of parties. You?

14:26.225 --> 14:29.393
Are you kidding? I'm all over that.
Hmm. What are you gonna wear?

14:29.394 --> 14:30.862
You want to know?

14:30.863 --> 14:33.765
You gotta show... To see
what I got going on.

14:37.970 --> 14:40.071
Hot on the case, Castle?

14:40.072 --> 14:43.407
On the case of a good read.
It's actually not bad.

14:43.408 --> 14:47.145
Esposito found
Morgan Lockerby.

14:47.146 --> 14:48.780
You mean...

14:48.781 --> 14:50.447
Morlock.

14:53.051 --> 14:55.753
Vixen was right.

14:55.754 --> 14:58.355
You smell like cherries.

14:58.356 --> 15:01.125
Hey, we got a hit on the...

15:01.126 --> 15:03.460
Are we interrupting something?

15:03.461 --> 15:05.663
Yes.
No.

15:05.664 --> 15:08.666
Okay.

15:08.667 --> 15:11.568
Wh-what'd you get
a hit on? (clears throat)

15:11.569 --> 15:14.872
The, uh, prints from
the stake in Crow's heart.

15:14.873 --> 15:17.241
Your girl Vixen was right.
Morgan Lockerby.

15:17.242 --> 15:20.477
Only thing is, he's one of
the great unfindables.

15:20.478 --> 15:22.780
No address, no phone number, no trail.

15:22.781 --> 15:24.515
Maybe not. Here.

15:24.516 --> 15:27.351
Recognize that corner?

15:27.352 --> 15:29.753
That's Broome and Clinton,
lower east side.

15:29.754 --> 15:33.257
I think Crow may have drawn us
a road map to Morlock.

