(sobs)

35:24.465 --> 35:26.832
(groans and whimpers)

35:26.833 --> 35:28.234
(Beckett) Here you go.

35:28.235 --> 35:29.869
Thank you.

35:34.542 --> 35:35.808
Why?

35:35.809 --> 35:37.810
She killed Elizabeth

35:37.811 --> 35:39.679
