to herself.

35:39.680 --> 35:42.549
And then she murdered Matthew
and his friend Daemon

35:42.550 --> 35:44.884
so that you would never find out.

35:44.885 --> 35:46.919
Matthew didn't know
who to trust,

35:46.920 --> 35:48.854
